{"type":"message","id":"be062588","parentId":"ff642aa8","timestamp":"2026-03-17T19:51:56.022Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, so following HEARTBEAT.md strictly:\n\n1. Memory-Check done - no open tasks in pending-tasks.md\n2. Since no tasks, I should generate ONE new task based on:\n   - Current projects (Git status)\n   - Open TODOs in code\n   - Improvements in workspace\n   - Learning opportunities\n\n3. This is the **first** heartbeat (checkCount: 0), so:\n   - Step 4 (Self-improvement every 3rd heartbeat) - NOT YET\n   - Step 5 (Project check every 5th heartbeat) - NOT YET\n\n4. I need to:\n   - Check git status for projects\n   - Look for TODOs in the code\n   - Generate ONE task\n   - Write to pending-tasks.md\n   - Send Telegram update\n   - Update heartbeat-state.json\n\nLet me check git status and look for TODOs first.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"**Heartbeat #1** — Checkliste wird abgearbeitet:\n\n1. ✅ **Memory-Check:** Keine offenen Aufgaben\n2. 🔄 **Aufgaben generieren:** Lese Projekte/TODOs..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:36","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/vboxuser/workspace && git status"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:37","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/vboxuser/workspace && grep -r \"TODO\\|FIXME\\|XXX\" --include=\"*.md\" --include=\"*.json\" . 2>/dev/null | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama_cloud","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773777111036}}
