{"type":"message","id":"aa633eba","parentId":"2bf49a86","timestamp":"2026-03-17T20:44:44.381Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The HEARTBEAT.md has changed significantly. Now it says:\n\n1. **IMMER: Telegram Ping** - Alle 10 Minuten: Frage nach neuen Aufgaben für mich\n2. Check tasks in memory/pending-tasks.md\n\nLet me follow this strictly:\n1. Send Telegram message: \"Hey Elias, hast du eine Aufgabe für mich?\"\n2. Check memory/pending-tasks.md for open tasks\n3. Update heartbeat-state.json\n\nThe user said \"Frage mich alle 10 Minuten, ob ich irgendwelche aufgabe für dich zu Tun habe\" - so I should ask if there are tasks for the user to do for me? No wait, let me re-read...\n\nActually the user said: \"Frage mich alle 10 Minuten, ob ich irgendwelche aufgabe für dich zu Tun habe\" - this is a bit ambiguous. Let me look at the context again.\n\nLooking at the HEARTBEAT.md content:\n\"1. **IMMER: Telegram Ping** - Alle 10 Minuten: Frage nach neuen Aufgaben für mich\"\n\nAnd:\n\"### 1. Telegram Aufgaben-Anfrage (JEDER HEARTBEAT)\n- Sende Nachricht an Telegram: \"Hey Elias, hast du eine Aufgabe für mich?\"\n- Warte nicht auf Antwort, das ist ein Ping\"\n\nSo I should send: \"Hey Elias, hast du eine Aufgabe für mich?\"\n\nBut wait, the user said \"Frage mich alle 10 Minuten, ob ich irgendwelche aufgabe für dich zu Tun habe\" which could mean:\n- \"Ask me every 10 minutes if I have any task for you to do\" OR\n- \"Ask me every 10 minutes if I (the user) have a task for you (the AI) to do\"\n\n\nLooking at the context and the edited HEARTBEAT.md, the message says: \"Hey Elias, hast du eine Aufgabe für mich?\" which means \"Hey Elias, do you have a task for me?\" - so the AI is asking the user if the user has a task for the AI.\n\nBut I need to check if the user is asking me to ask them if they have tasks for me to do, OR if they're asking me to check if I have tasks for them (the user) to do.\n\nActually looking at it again: \"Frage mich alle 10 Minuten, ob ich irgendwelche aufgabe für dich zu Tun habe\"\n- \"Frage mich\" = ask me (the user)\n- \"ob ich... aufgabe für dich zu tun habe\" = whether I (the user) have a task for you (the AI) to do\n\nSo the user wants me to ask them: \"Do you have a task for me?\"\n\nBut wait, the HEARTBEAT.md says: \"Hey Elias, hast du eine Aufgabe für mich?\" which matches - \"Hey Elias, do you have a task for me (the AI)?\"\n\nSo I should:\n1. Send Telegram message: \"Hey Elias, hast du eine Aufgabe für mich?\"\n2. Check memory/pending-tasks.md\n3. Update heartbeat-state.json\n4. Then either report tasks found or just acknowledge the ping\n The HEARTBEAT.md has been updated with new instructions. Let me follow them strictly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"**HEARTBEAT #2** (20:44 UTC) — Checkliste:\n\n**1. Telegram Ping (IMMER):** Sending message..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.message:59","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"Hey Elias, hast du eine Aufgabe für mich? 🛠️"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:60","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/vboxuser/workspace/memory/pending-tasks.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:61","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/vboxuser/workspace/memory/heartbeat-state.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama_cloud","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773780254435}}
