{"type":"message","id":"8da287a4","parentId":"4e7f0fdd","timestamp":"2026-03-17T20:45:03.357Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Telegram send failed with \"chat not found\" error. I should:\n1. Note the error but continue with the rest of the heartbeat\n2. Check for tasks in pending-tasks.md - there are none (empty)\n3. Update the heartbeat-state.json\n\nSince the Telegram ping failed but I need to report this, I should not send HEARTBEAT_OK. Let me report what happened:\n- Telegram ping: FAILED (chat not found)\n- Tasks check: No open tasks\n- Should I send HEARTBEAT_OK? According to the rules: \"Niemals bei aktivem HEARTBEAT_OK, wenn Telegram-Ping gesendet wurde\" - since I tried to send but it failed, this is not a normal OK situation.\n\nActually, since the ping failed and there are no tasks, I should report the status but it's not purely \"nothing to do\" - there was an error with the Telegram send.\n\nLet me update the state and report: Wait, the Telegram send failed. Let me update the state and report the status:\n\n1. Telegram ping: FAILED (chat not found)\n2. Tasks: None found","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.edit:62","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/vboxuser/workspace/memory/heartbeat-state.json","old_string":"{\n  \"lastChecks\": {\n    \"email\": null,\n    \"calendar\": null,\n    \"memoryReview\": \"2026-03-17T20:11:00Z\",\n    \"skillsReview\": null,\n    \"gitStatus\": \"2026-03-17T20:11:00Z\",\n    \"trading\": null\n  },\n  \"cyclesCompleted\": 1\n}","new_string":"{\n  \"lastChecks\": {\n    \"email\": null,\n    \"calendar\": null,\n    \"memoryReview\": \"2026-03-17T20:11:00Z\",\n    \"skillsReview\": null,\n    \"gitStatus\": \"2026-03-17T20:11:00Z\",\n    \"trading\": null\n  },\n  \"cyclesCompleted\": 2,\n  \"hasTasks\": false,\n  \"lastPing\": \"2026-03-17T20:44:00Z\",\n  \"pingStatus\": \"failed_chat_not_found\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","prov