{"type":"message","id":"faac029d","parentId":"d9ca39c7","timestamp":"2026-03-17T20:45:06.853Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, so the Telegram ping failed with \"chat not found\". I should report this as it's an error/important finding. According to the HEARTBEAT.md, I should always report:\n- Telegram Ping (this is an alert)\n- Tasks found (if any)\n\nSince the Telegram ping failed, this is something importantto report.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"**Heartbeat-Status #2** (20:44 UTC):\n\n📨 **Telegram Ping:** ❌ Fehlgeschlagen — Chat nicht gefunden (Telegram-Config prüfen!)\n\n📋 **Aufgaben-Check:** Keine offenen Aufgaben in `memory/pending-tasks.md`\n\n⏱️ **State aktualisiert:** cyclesCompleted: 2, hasTasks: false\n\n---\n\n**Hinweis:** Der Telegram-Ping hat nicht funktioniert. Muss die Telegram-Konfiguration in OpenClaw geprüft werden? (`openclaw config` oder Gateway-Einstellungen)"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama_cloud","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773780303362}}
