{"type":"message","id":"e9f9ee55","parentId":"458facff","timestamp":"2026-03-17T21:13:10.298Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has received a heartbeat at 21:13 UTC. According to the instructions and the HEARTBEAT.md, I need to:\n\n1. Read HEARTBEAT.md from the workspace\n2. Follow it strictly\n3. Check for tasks in memory/pending-tasks.md\n4. Send a Telegram ping asking for tasks\n5. Update the heartbeat-state.json\n\nLet me execute the heartbeat checklist according to the updated HEARTBEAT.md which includes:\n- ALWAYS: Telegram Ping - Ask for new tasks every 10 minutes\n- Task Check - Check memory/pending-tasks.md for open tasks\n\nSince this is a heartbeat, I should:\n1. Send the Telegram message: \"Hey Elias, hast du eine Aufgabe für mich?\"\n2. Check pending-tasks.md\n3. Update heartbeat-state.json\n4. Report what I found\n\nThe user wants me to always report what I'm doing during heartbeats.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:92","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/vboxuser/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:93","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/vboxuser/workspace/memory/pending-tasks.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:94","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/vboxuser/workspace/memory/heartbeat-state.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama_cloud","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773781984954}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac7ad23f","parentId":"e9f9ee55","timestamp":"2026-03-17T21:13:10.306Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.read:92","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Autonomous Tasks\n\n## Overview\nThis file configures periodic tasks that run every ~10 minutes via heartbeat mechanism.\nAgent should read this file and execute the checklist.\n\n## When to Trigger Alerts (send to user)\n1. **IMMER: Telegram Ping** - Alle 10 Minuten: Frage nach neuen Aufgaben für mich\n2. **Aufgaben vorhanden** - Offene Tasks in `memory/pending-tasks.md` gefunden\n3. **Email**: Urgent unread messages (flagged/marked important)\n4. **Calendar**: Events starting within next 2 hours\n5. **Trading**: Significant price movements (if configured)\n6. **Errors**: Failed autonomous tasks or stuck processes\n\n## Background Work (silent, no alert unless error)\nRotate through these tasks, ~2-4 per heartbeat cycle:\n\n### 1. Telegram Aufgaben-Anfrage (JEDER HEARTBEAT)\n- Sende Nachricht an Telegram: \"Hey Elias, hast du eine Aufgabe für mich?\"\n- Warte nicht auf Antwort, das ist ein Ping\n\n### 2. Aufgaben-Check (JEDER HEARTBEAT)\n- Lese `memory/pending-tasks.md`\n- Gibt es offene `[ ]` Aufgaben?\n- Wenn JA → Setze in `memory/heartbeat-state.json`:`\"hasTasks\": true`\n- Wenn NEIN → `\"hasTasks\": false`\n\n### Daily Rotation (track in memory/heartbeat-state.json)\n- Check email for unread/important\n- Check calendar for upcoming events\n- Review memory/ files from last 7 days, update MEMORY.md\n- Review own skills for improvement opportunities\n- Check workspace git status, commit if needed\n- Review TODO items in memory/todo.md\n\n### Trading Analysis (if configured)\n- Check portfolio/watchlist\n- Analyze price movements\n- Update trading journal\n\n### Skill Development\n- Identify gaps in current skills\n- Research new skill ideas\n- Document learnings\n\n## Output\n- **IMMER: Telegram Ping** - Jeder Heartbeat: \"Hey Elias, hast du eine Aufgabe für mich?\"\n- **Wenn Aufgaben gefunden** - Liste die offenen Tasks auf\n- Important findings: ACTIVE ALERT to user\n- Routine work: Log to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md silently\n- Errors: Log to memory/errors.md with timestamp\n\n## NO_REPLY (HEARTBEAT_OK) Rules\n- Niemals bei aktivem HEARTBEAT_OK, wenn Telegram-Ping gesendet wurde\n- Nur HEARTBEAT_OK wenn explizit nichts zu tun und kein Ping nötig\n\n## Tracking\nMaintain state in: memory/heartbeat-state.json\n```json\n{\n  \"lastChecks\": {\n    \"email\": null,\n    \"calendar\": null,\n    \"memoryReview\": null,\n    \"skillsReview\": null,\n    \"gitStatus\": null,\n    \"trading\": null\n  },\n  \"cyclesCompleted\": 0\n}\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773781990305}}
{"type":"message","id":"70565cd7","parentId":"ac7ad23f","timestamp":"2026-03-17T21:13:10.307Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.read:93","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pending Tasks - Aufgaben-Queue\n\n**Letzte Aktualisierung:** 2026-03-17\n\n## Aktive Aufgaben\n\n- [x] Die 20 nützlichsten Skills finden und zum Workspace hinzufügen (Priorität: Hoch)\n  - ✅ Suche in OpenClaw Skills-Verzeichnis\n  - ✅ Identifiziere Top 20+ basierend auf Nützlichkeit  \n  - ✅ Kopiert zu `/home/vboxuser/workspace/skills/`\n  - ✅ README.md mit Übersicht erstellt\n\n## Abgeschlossene Aufgaben (heute)\n\n- [x] README.md Test-Datei erstellt (Tools-Test)\n\n## Warteschlange (nächste Ideen)\n\n*Wird bei Bedarf gefüllt*\n\n---\n\n**Wie Aufgaben hinzufügen:**\nEinfach unter \"Aktive Aufgaben\" eintragen:\n```markdown\n- [ ] Aufgabenbeschreibung (Priorität: Hoch/Mittel/Niedrig)\n  - Details...\n  - Deadline: optional\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773781990306}}
